  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "<b>Log #36: </b> Subject 44 has shown to able of critical thinking and
    self-awarness. So far it has been the stablest long-term fusion between CCBU
    [1] and Organic Matter, avoiding the previous experiments high rates of organic
    decay.\n\nWhile the results so far are to be considered prolific, experiments
    on the subject will continue to verify this is not a fluke.\n\n<u> To Note</u>: 
    the longer the subject is in cryogenic state, it's behaviour has shown to be
    more agressive toward the scientists in general. Current hypothesis is that its
    brain activity is not as suspended as the monitors results have shown. \n"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: d9c367d619c15f5469ec6fc73a136211, type: 2}
